@startuml REQ-PROD-001 Device Environmental Monitoring
autonumber

box "System" #LightBlue
  participant "Sensor Driver" as Sensor_Driver
  participant "Controller" as Controller
  participant "Comm Manager" as Comm_Manager
end box

header
  **REQ-PROD-001: Device Environmental Monitoring**
  //Description:// The system shall continuously monitor temperature and humidity and report to cloud.
  //Acceptance Criteria:// Sensor readings aggregated and transmitted. Cloud receives telemetry within reporting interval.
end header


Sensor_Driver --> Controller: EVENT:SENSOR_DATA_READY\nSensor_ReadTemperature() → Controller_OnSensorData()
note right of Controller: THRESHOLD_CHECK
alt (sensor_value > threshold)
Controller --> Controller: EVENT:CONTROL_ACTION\nController_OnSensorData() → Controller_ReportStatus()
Controller -> Comm_Manager: Comm_SendStatus()
end alt
Sensor_Driver --> Controller: EVENT:SENSOR_DATA_READY\nSensor_ReadHumidity() → Controller_OnSensorData()

@enduml